        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 13.— Illustration of identification key for Cichlidogyrus Paperna,1960 species:A, shape of the penis (spirally coiled [a], not spirally coiled [b]); B, number of turns in spirally coiled penis and shape of the sclerotised vagina (4-5 and sinuous [a], more than 4-5 and spirally coiled [b]); C, number of turns in spirally coiled penis (8-9 [a], 14-15 [b]); D, penis diameter (large [a], filiform [b]); E, shape of the penis (straight [a], curved [b]); F, shape of the penis (G [a], single looped [b])." ;
