        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 1. — Definition of characters used in the identification keys of Cichlidogyrus Paperna, 1960 species (from 54 species studied): A, value repartition of the standardised length of dorsal transverse bar auricles; B, value repartition of the standardised length of uncinuli pairs III-VII;C, value repartition of the standardised length of uncinuli pair I." ;
