<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4520443>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 12. — Illustration of identification key for Cichlidogyrus Paperna, 1960 species: A, shape of the accessory piece base (gutter-like [a], narrow [b]); B, presence (a) or absence (b) of a round bulge at distal third of the accessory piece; C, shape of the accessory piece ending (double [a], single [b]); D, shape of the accessory piece ending hook (thin and long [a], wide and short [b]); E, shape of penis heel (wide [a], narrow [b]); F, shape of penis extremity and accessory piece (folded back and close C [a], straight and open C [b]); G, size of accessory piece (long [a], short [b])." ;
